The results on instance-annotated CoQuAD and natural Questions dataset are in Table (ref). We see that GoogleSDA is the best across datasets in terms of MAP and AR. {\mysystem} comes close in the CoQuAD dataset but performs worse than both baselines in the Natural Questions dataset. Instance explanations when readily available in KGs can be extracted with a single query. Texts prove useful when KG is incomplete or the SPARQL translation is not capture the user intent. We test this hypothesis in the next sub-section.